    <div class="cell is-col-span-8 mt-6">
      <h3 class="subtitle is-5 has-text-weight-bold"> API Endpoint: Art Institute of Chicago - Exhibitions</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="cell is-col-span-8">
      <p>
        This REST API endpoint returns JSON-formatted data. Each entry describes an exhibition,
        including the title, description, when they started and ended, as well as which gallery
        it featured in primarily. This endpoint includes a subresource of related artworks,
        which is described next.
      </p>
    </div>

