    <div class="cell is-col-span-8 mt-6">
      <h3 class="subtitle is-5 has-text-weight-bold"> API Endpoint: Art Institute of Chicago - Artworks</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="cell is-col-span-8">
      <p>
        This REST API endpoint returns JSON-formatted data. Instead of calling it by itself, this information
        is collected through the exhibition endpoint as related artworks. This is the main source of data,
        and is being used to create around 150 artwork records for the database. The information being
        collected is the name of the piece, date it was created, medium, place of origin, dimensions,
        description, and alt text for images. This endpoint also holds information needed to find related
        artists and images.
      </p>
    </div>

