    <div class="cell is-col-span-8 mt-6">
      <h3 class="subtitle is-5 has-text-weight-bold"> Added Data: Categories</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="cell is-col-span-8">
      <p>
        This is not an API endpoint, but actually just collected terms from the artwork endpoint. It's
        collected and separated into a separate database table to have a reduced list of categories
        to be referenced by artworks. It also allows us to look into specific categories without searching
        through the artwork layer first. A category can range from describing the art period, eg.
        Contemporary, to the medium, eg. Prints and Drawings, or even a location.
      </p>
    </div>

