    <div class="cell is-col-span-8 mt-6">
      <h3 class="subtitle is-5 has-text-weight-bold"> API Endpoint: Art Institute of Chicago - Images</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="cell is-col-span-8">
      <p>
        This REST API endpoint returns an image when specifications are added at the end for size, region,
        rotation, quality, and file type. The image id is found in the artwork request, and requested
        individually. If the specifications are not added, it returns JSON-formatted data that describes
        the size options and colours of the image. The images collected are stored using Active Storage.
      </p>
    </div>

